Idea: Create a video streaming website like chatroulette with random people. 
      The difference is that we will allow users to select catagories/topics of discussion. 

Functionalities: 
- Allow for video streaming and text box
  - 2 people for now. Later add functionality for 2-6 people
- topics/catagories
  - No topic
  - random/quick search
  - Sports
  - News
  - Custom - related search. Keyword search.
- Number of people in in the category
- accounts 
  - So that people can become friend or report inappropriate activities
- Advance search
- Location search
